QuestData.Title: Operation: Just Arrowhead
QuestData.Description: It goes without saying that we'll help you kill any of the Warsong out in the open down there.$B$BYou just start the fight, and we'll end it with extreme prejudice.
QuestData.RewardText: That bit of justice is sure to have lifted the spirits of my rangari.$B$BLosing Telaar and many of our friends has taken a heavy toll.$B$BThank you, commander.
